<a name="2.3.1"></a><a name="selenium" class="headingAnchor"></a><h4>2.3.1 Selenium</h4>
<p>The Selenium diagram is dedicated to the Selenium Grid component of Mailchecker.
It outlines the structure and functionality of the Selenium Grid, including the Metrics Exporter,
Selenium Hub, and Nodes, which play a vital role in rendering web pages for Carts content analysis
and screenshots.</p>
