<a name="2.3.2"></a><a name="deployment" class="headingAnchor"></a><h4>2.3.2 Deployment</h4>
<p>The deployment of Mailchecker is a critical aspect of its overall architecture, ensuring that the application
is scalable, reliable, and efficient. The deployment strategy is designed to leverage cloud-based infrastructure,
specifically Google Cloud, and container orchestration using Kubernetes (K8S). This approach not only enhances the
application's performance but also provides flexibility and resilience in its operation.</p>
